# {{ project_name }}

Infrastructure of **{{ community_name }}** — an agent-operable GitOps stack
with central single sign-on, generated from
[agentops-community-stack](https://github.com/levino/agentops-community-stack).

```
Internet :80/:443 → {{ server_ipv4 }}
  └── k3s + Traefik (hostPort)
        ├── cert-manager        → TLS via ACME (issuer: acme)
        ├── sealed-secrets      → secrets encrypted in git
        ├── Flux                → this repo is the truth
        ├── ZITADEL             → id.{{ domain }} (one identity per person)
        └── apps                → one namespace each (apps/)
```

